dc_title_s: Map of Atlantic Ocean and Barnegat Bay from Bay Head to Barnegat Light showing the exterior lines established thereon by the Riparian Commission of New Jersey
dc_description_s: This map depicts the exterior lines in red ink along the length of Long Beach Island from Bayhead to Barnegat Light, as determined by the New Jersey State RIparian Commission. The map is ink on tracing paper.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
